parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The electrical system failure can cause a fire to break out in the vehicle, potentially leading to injuries, fatalities, and property damage.
symptoms: Yellow smoke billowing out from under the glovebox on the passenger side
fire flames between the dash and window
melting of the passenger side under glove box area and ABS floor
re-ignition of the fire after being initially put out.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The unavailability of parts for recall repairs can leave vehicles with safety-critical issues on the road, potentially leading to accidents, injuries, or fatalities.
symptoms: Notification of a recall
but parts are not available
and the manufacturer is unable to confirm when they will become available.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Transmission Failure due to Water Damage
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Water damage in the trunk can cause transmission failure, leading to deceleration, inability to shift gears, and loss of power, which can increase the risk of accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle decelerates unexpectedly
the transmission warning light illuminates
the vehicle fails to shift into gear
loss of power
delay in acceleration.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Camshaft Failure causing Delayed Acceleration and Loss of Power
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Camshaft failure can cause delayed acceleration, loss of power, and illumination of the check engine light, which can lead to accidents or make the vehicle difficult to control.
symptoms: Delayed acceleration
loss of power
check engine light illuminates while driving or stationary.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Intake Camshaft Position Slow Response (Bank 2) and Oil Pump Activation Limit Value Exceeded
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the intake camshaft position sensor and oil pump activation can cause the engine to stall, leading to a loss of power and control, which can increase the risk of accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The engine stalls without warning
the engine indicator illuminates
the check engine indicator remains illuminated after restarting the vehicle
diagnostic trouble codes P000C and P1538 are present.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The glare from the dashboard reflection on the windshield can cause temporary blindness, increasing the risk of accidents, especially during sunny days.
symptoms: The dashboard reflection on the windshield obstructs the driver's view
making it difficult to see while driving
especially during sunny days.
